IN THE CAFETERIA ?

13:22.800 --> 13:24.097
UH, YEAH.

13:24.100 --> 13:26.853
ACTUALLY,
IT'S JUST LIKE THAT.

13:26.860 --> 13:28.919
AND THEN ?

13:28.930 --> 13:34.152
AND THEN ONCE
THE BODY IS IN THERE,

13:34.160 --> 13:36.549
THEN THERE'S A BUTTON
THAT'S PRESSED.

13:36.560 --> 13:37.788
SOUNDS GOOD.

13:37.800 --> 13:39.256
EVEN THOUGH THE GOOD RABBI
SAID I SHOULDN'T,

13:39.260 --> 13:40.852
JUST BURN ME UP.

13:40.860 --> 13:42.896
WHO PUSHES THE BUTTON ?

13:42.900 --> 13:44.595
WHOMEVER YOU SPECIFY.

13:44.600 --> 13:46.898
