A FAMILY MEMBER.

13:46.900 --> 13:48.754
AND THEN SOME PEOPLE
CHOOSE NO ONE,

13:48.760 --> 13:50.853
IN WHICH CASE THE PERSON WHO
WORKS AT THE CREMATORY DOES IT.

13:50.860 --> 13:52.498
I'LL TAKE THAT GUY.

13:53.860 --> 13:57.159
I GUESS I'LL BE ON MY OWN
AT THAT POINT, THOUGH.

13:57.160 --> 14:01.358
WHAT ABOUT FAMILY MEMBERS,
YOUR PARENTS ?

14:01.360 --> 14:04.659
