TO STOP COMING.

14:06.200 --> 14:08.293
THEY'LL FIND OUT I'M DEAD
WHEN THE REST OF THE WORLD DOES.

14:08.300 --> 14:11.098
ANY OTHER FRIENDS ?

14:11.100 --> 14:14.649
YEAH, I HAD SOME,
A LOT OF WORK, YOU KNOW ?

14:14.660 --> 14:17.151
